description:
On today's episode's of the Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps Thursday Night's game between the Panthers and Falcons. Are the Falcons the best 2 win team we've seen? We're joined by Falcons QB Matt Ryan, PTI's Mike Wilbon, College Football Play by Play announcer Chris Fowler, and Dodgers Manager Dave Roberts. Plus, Fritzy shares his Halloween Sports Names.
